Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:24.92,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mazen na! Kiken da!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:27.59,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Yatsura ga aisurya dotanba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.34,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dontanba ja nai ka
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:32.64,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mazeru na! Kiken no nengoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:40.70,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dotanba tte no sono wake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:43.77,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Sorya maa yatsu ga deatte kara darou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:46.19,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Tanonja nai shomondai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:49.24,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Maneku kakeawasette no aru no da
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.24,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mou au koto wo tomerya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:54.45,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Sore de koto wa sumu wake da keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:56.70,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Iya ni naru you na ki ga tsukya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:59.91,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Futari bocchi nan na no karuma kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:05.46,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mazeru na! Somosomo deau na!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.74,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Torisetsu ni sa dondake kaitetemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:13.47,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Muda saa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.10,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mazen na! Kiken da!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.85,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Yatsura ga aisurya dotanba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:21.48,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dontanba kamau ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:23.86,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Somosomo hitotsu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:26.86,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mazen na! Kiken da!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:29.57,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Yatsura ga aisurya dotanba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:32.07,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dontanba kamau ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.07,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Sorosoro ikou ze meifu madou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:24.92,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nepleť se do toho! Je to nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:27.59,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dojde-li ke spojení, zahnán budeš do kouta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.34,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Jsi už v koutě zahnaný!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:32.64,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nepleť se do toho! Je to nebezpečné setkání!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:40.70,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Důvod, proč jsi zahnán do kouta?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:43.77,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}S prominutím, příčinou je vaše setkání
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:46.19,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}To je ta křižovatka
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:49.24,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Co ti způsobuje problémy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.24,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Pokud jim zabráníme v setkání
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:54.41,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Tak bude vše v pořádku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:57.05,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Špatný pocit z toho mám a když jsem si to uvědomil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:59.91,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ti dva byli spolu. Je to karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:05.46,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nepleť se do toho! Nemluv s nimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.74,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Na manuálu tolik nesejde
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:13.47,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Je to zbytečné
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.10,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nepleť se do toho! Je to nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.85,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dojde-li ke spojení, zahnán budeš do kouta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:21.48,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Záleží ti na klidném životě?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:23.86,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}S tím měl jsi začít
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:26.86,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nepleť se do toho! Je to nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:29.57,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Pokud se spojí, budeš zahnán do kouta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:32.07,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Záleží ti na klidném životě?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.07,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nastal čas jít do tajemné říše mrtvých
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:25.74,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kyoufu ni obietatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:29.45,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Uchikatsu hodo no taori wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:32.87,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Omottau koto warashite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:36.25,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Yami ni hikari uedoshite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.92,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Michibikarete sentaku shite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:43.51,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mizu kara eranda michi na noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.51,0:22:47.22,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mayoi doori saa mayottari nayandari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:51.23,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Demo iku shikanai darou tatoe subete kaketemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:55.73,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Zutto kakko mo ima mo mirai mo kanarazu ni motteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:59.48,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dare ni mo makenai tsuyoi ishi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:03.03,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Owari koto mo naku susumu kimetai ten toppa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:07.66,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Zetsubou wo kibou ni kaete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:11.70,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hero nanpaku tachi agare
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:15.00,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hero mamorou jishin sa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:19.05,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kitto Rival to tomo ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:23.68,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,500)}Fusion chikara no hitotsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:25.74,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Strachem jsem ochromen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:29.45,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ale nikdy zcela nevyhraje
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:32.87,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kvůli tomu jsem rozhodnut se smát
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:36.25,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Přinést světlo do temnoty
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.92,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mé rozhodnutí mě vede
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:43.51,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I když je to cesta osamělá
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.51,0:22:47.22,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I když jsem na pochybách
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:51.23,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Stále jdu směrem kupředu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:55.73,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Beru sebou touhu nikdy nikoho neztratit
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:59.48,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ať už minulou, současnou nebo budoucí
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:03.03,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Překonám tuto nekonečnou cestu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:07.66,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}A přeměním zoufalství v naději
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:11.70,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Možné je, že hrdina povstane
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:15.00,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Je to on, kdo vás bude chránit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:19.05,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}A proti soupeřům, kterým se postaví
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:23.68,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,500)}Použije sílu přátelství
